===============================================================================

After creating your work you may wish to:

  1. Customize the show page:

      In /app/views/hyrax/your_works
      edit _attribute_rows.html.erb
      eg. to add render_as:

  2. Customize facets and search results

      With DogBiscuits:
        by configuring properties and required properties
            in config/initializers/dog_biscuits.rb:
        by changing the index display
            in config/dog_biscuits.yml
        and re-running rails g dog_biscuits:catalog_controller
        (this will overwrite any changes to catalog_controller)

      Or, directly in app/controllers/catalog_controller.rb
          edit the config.add_facet_field
          edit the config.add_index_field
          eg. to change order and add new local properties

  3. Further modify the model, actor, form or presenter,

      eg. with locally defined properties.

  To add a local property the dog_biscuits way:

      add to the model, form, presenter and solr_document
      add labels and help text to config/locales/

      add to config/initializers/dog_biscuits.rb

      re_generate schema_org with:
        rails g dog_biscuits:schema_org -f
      re_generate catalog_controller.rb with:
        rails g dog_biscuits:catalog_controller -f
      re_generate _attribute_rows.html.erb with:
        rails g dog_biscuits:attribute_rows -f

===============================================================================